{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/text4.png?t=1732368977\" />You are an unlikely hero going on an adventure across islands in the sky. It's dangerous to go alone - your trusty Book of Summons will keep you company. Day or night, sunshine or rain, explore each island your way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/About_Image_copy_13.png?t=1732368977\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/text2.png?t=1732368977\" />Collect and smash Crystals to add monsters to your party. Summon them in real-time, hack and slash battles. You don't need to rely on them to do all the fighting either. Armed with a stick, you can damage enemies to maximise summon time, and also heal and buff your summons.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/About_Image_copy_11.png?t=1732368977\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/text1.png?t=1732368977\" />Upgrade your summons' abilities with the materials your've found on your travels. Take your pick from Fire, Ice, Air and Earth. Can't choose? Why not level them all up?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/About_Image_copy_4.png?t=1732368977\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2784310/extras/text3.png?t=1732368977\" />Meet new friends and other travellers to uncover th